<p>Denise is the author of <i><a href="http://cssdetectiveguide.com/">The CSS Detective Guide</a></i> and a co-author for <i><a href="http://interactwithwebstandards.com/">InterAct With Web Standards: A Holistic Approach to Web Design</a></i>. She travels around the world to speak at prestigious conferences about all things web-related, from Creativity and Creative Inspiration, CSS3 best practices to Responsive Design. When she is not writing articles for influential publications such as <a href="http://www.alistapart.com/">A List Apart</a>, <a href="http://www.netmagazine.com/">.net Magazine</a> and <a href="http://www.smashingmagazine.com/">Smashing Magazine</a>, Denise is a Web Design Trainer and Consultant at her own company, PapillonEffect.</p>
<p>You can check her website <a href="http://denisejacobs.com/">DeniseJacobs.com</a> and follow her on Twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/denisejacobs">@denisejacobs</a>.</p>